        <h1>How to Fix the Colors in your TV Picture</h1>
    </header>
        <p>First we need to rule out the possibility that the problem could be coming from the source. Change the channel or switch to another input or signal source and see if the color problem goes away. If it does, then the problem may very well be the TV station or the broadcast network.</p>
